      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting with my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, this beauty is in such incredible shape, you'd swear it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been garage-kept, meticulously cared for, and drives like a total dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for a new home, this is the one. Come see it for yourself\u2014you won\u2019t be disappointed!",
