      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a concours-level E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. This example boasts a meticulously maintained double VANOS system and a perfectly shimmed valvetrain, ensuring peak volumetric efficiency. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, while the variable M-differential lock ensures optimal torque distribution. Proactively maintained, the chassis has undergone full subframe reinforcement, and the suspension retains its factory-fresh damping characteristics. This is a mechanically transparent, investment-grade specimen with zero deferred maintenance, presenting in showroom condition for the most exacting collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
