      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the showroom floor. This meticulously maintained masterpiece has been exclusively garage-kept and hand-washed, preserving a deep, mirror-like finish on the exterior without a single stone chip or swirl mark in sight. Step inside to an interior that still carries that new-car aroma; the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of any creases, while every digital interface and tactile button remains in flawless working order. Under the hood, the engine bay is spotless, reflecting a rigorous adherence to every scheduled service interval\u2014all documented in a comprehensive history folder. With ultra-low mileage and a clean title, this car represents a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands perfection. It is, quite simply, the finest example of its kind currently available on the market.",
